%20called%20this%20type%20of%20breathing%20%26quot%3Bgear%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20breathing%20in%20through%20the%20nose%20and%20out%20through%20the%20mouth%20%26quot%3Bgear%20two.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20told%20to%20note%20when%20we%20had%20to%20%26quot%3Bswitch%20gears.%26quot%3B%20Iskandarani%20said%20this%20should%20happen%20after%20around%2090-seconds%20to%20two-minutes%2C%20but%20I%20struggled%20to%20get%20to%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20rough%20guide%2C%20the%20longer%20you%20can%20stay%20in%20gear%20one%2C%20the%20higher%20your%20VO2%20max%20is%20likely%20to%20be%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%2C%20over%20time%2C%20you%20will%20need%20to%20switch%20gears%20less%20quickly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshort-workout-improve-fitness-exercise-snacks-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20indicates%20your%20aerobic%20capacity%20has%20increased%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20halfway%20through%20the%20class%2C%20we%20were%20given%20nasal%20strips%20to%20stick%20on%20the%20fleshy%20part%20of%20our%20noses%2C%20and%20encouraged%20to%20notice%20if%20it%20helped%20us%20stay%20in%20gear%20one%20for%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20thought%20that%20widening%20the%20nasal%20canal%20could%20help%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fhow-often-should-you-do-cardio%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincrease%20endurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20allowing%20more%20air%20through%20the%20nose.%20But%20one%202020%20meta-analysis%20published%20in%20the%20European%20Archives%20of%20Oto-Rhino-Laryngology%20found%20that%20wearing%20a%20nasal%20strip%20while%20exercising%20didn't%20improve%20VO2%20Max%20or%20heart%20rate.%20Still%2C%20lots%20of%20runners%20and%20athletes%20swear%20by%20them%2C%20like%20the%20elite%20tennis%20player%20Carlos%20Alcaraz%2C%20who%20wears%20them%20during%20his%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20that%20the%20nasal%20strip%20helped%20a%20little%2C%20but%20it%20kept%20peeling%20off%20as%20my%20nose%20got%20sweaty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb33c79c-8ac8-48a6-b10e-431e58917996%5C%22%3EBreathing%20through%20your%20nose%20while%20exercising%20is%20thought%20to%20help%20you%20stay%20in%20Zone%202%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENasal%20breathing%20is%20not%20directly%20linked%20to%20improving%20VO2%20max%2C%20but%20is%20thought%20to%20help%20the%20body%20use%20oxygen%20more%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20encourages%20you%20to%20stay%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheart-rate-training-benefits-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZone%202%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20at%2060-70%25%20of%20your%20maximum%20heart%20rate%2C%20while%20you're%20exercising.%20Your%20muscles%20have%20more%20access%20to%20oxygen%20in%20Zone%202%2C%20making%20it%20an%20effective%20way%20to%20increase%20aerobic%20endurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20enter%20Zone%203%2C%2070%25%20to%2080%25%20of%20your%20max%20heart%20rate%2C%20you're%20moving%20at%20an%20intensity%20that's%20too%20much%20for%20the%20available%20oxygen%20supply%2C%20which%20causes%20you%20to%20get%20out%20of%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eff962d2-b0c3-497c-abaf-4dc4a98298d3%5C%22%3EBreathing%20through%20my%20nose%20and%20doing%20cardio%20at%20the%20same%20time%20was%20hard%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20to%20remember%20and%20focus%20on%20in%20this%20class%3A%20not%20only%20understanding%20the%20different%20gears%2C%20but%20trying%20to%20stay%20in%20gear%20one%20while%20checking%20the%20clock%20to%20see%20when%20I%20started%20mouth%20breathing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20mental%20arithmetic%20was%20required%20on%20top%20of%20the%20three-minute%20sets%20of%20cardio%2C%20which%2C%20I%20think%20is%20fair%20to%20say%2C%20is%20a%20long%20time.%20My%20mind%20kept%20wandering%20and%20I%20kept%20accidentally%20mouth%20breathing%20before%20I'd%20actually%20reached%20my%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20tricky%20to%20go%20at%20a%20slow%20enough%20pace%20to%20stay%20in%20gear%20one%20for%20even%20a%20minute.%20After%20about%20thirty%20seconds%20I%20started%20to%20lose%20my%20breath.%20I%20suppose%20that%20tells%20me%20I%20have%20some%20work%20to%20do%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20I%20wasn't%20huffing%20and%20puffing%20or%20red%20in%20the%20face%20afterwards%20like%20I%20usually%20am%20after%20a%2035-minute%20run.%20But%20my%20arms%20did%20get%20very%20tired%20from%20pulling%20the%20ropes%20on%20the%20ski%20machine%20and%20moving%20the%20handles%20on%20the%20assault%20bike%20back%20and%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20uses%20a%20ski%20machine%20in%20a%20gym.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687670c685e81483682e086a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20class%20lasted%20around%20an%20hour.%3Cp%3EKim%20Schewitz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d4cbefe-5f25-40c2-986c-dd29e4217cdf%5C%22%3EA%20structured%20class%20made%20working%20on%20my%20cardio%20feel%20more%20achievable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20did%20this%20class%20again%20I%20would%20pace%20myself%20better%20so%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20get%20out%20of%20breath%20so%20quickly.%20But%20I%20think%20for%20a%20cardio%20beginner%20like%20me%2C%20it%20was%20a%20little%20too%20technical%20and%20advanced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIskandarani%20said%20that%20part%20of%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20class%20came%20from%20Hyrox%20fans%20and%20CrossFitters%2C%20who%20are%20already%20pretty%20fit%20and%20looking%20to%20increase%20their%20endurance%20for%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20found%20doing%20cardio%20in%20such%20a%20structured%20way%20and%20with%20a%20group%20of%20people%20much%20more%20fun%20and%20motivating%20than%20doing%20it%20alone.%20Going%20forward%2C%20I%20think%20I'll%20stick%20to%20cardio%20classes%20rather%20than%20running%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20getting%20bored%2C%20and%20trying%20again%20when%20enough%20time%20has%20passed%20for%20me%20to%20forget%20how%20arduous%20I%20found%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20focusing%20on%20my%20breath%2C%20it%20became%20apparent%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flower-cancer-risk-exercise-cardio-fitness-study-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecardiovascular%20fitness%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20lower%20than%20I'd%20like%2C%20and%20I'm%20only%2028.%20I%20wondered%20how%20it%20would%20inevitably%20deteriorate%20over%20time%2C%20and%20if%20I'm%20struggling%20to%20get%20through%20a%20class%20like%20this%20now%2C%20it's%20only%20going%20to%20get%20harder%20when%20I'm%20in%20my%2050s%2C%20let%20alone%2080s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20VO2%20max%20workout%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20was%20the%20right%20cardio%20class%20for%20me%2C%20but%20it's%20motivated%20me%20to%20continue%20my%20search.%20Anyone%20for%20Zumba%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincrease-vo2-max-fitness-class-review-make-cardio-fun-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752612116000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687671bdf748d8c055f5a27f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincrease-vo2-max-fitness-class-review-make-cardio-fun-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20cardio%20class%20to%20increase%20VO2%20max%2C%20which%20a%20Business%20Insider%20health%20reporter%20tried%2C%20involved%20wearing%20a%20nasal%20strip%20and%20breathing%20through%20her%20mouth%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincrease-vo2-max-fitness-class-review