rn-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-470121%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20started%20to%20experiment%20with%20permaculture%20once%20he%20moved%20to%20his%20farm%20near%20Pamidi%20in%20Anantapur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArriving%20at%20the%20farm%20was%20both%20relief%20and%20reckoning.%20He%20remembers%20the%20parched%20soil%2C%20the%20dry%20well%2C%20and%20the%20overgrown%20stream%20bed.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20a%20lush%20paradise.%20But%20I%20did%20not%20want%20a%20traditional%20farm%20either%2C%20so%20this%20worked%20out%20for%20me.%20I%20wanted%20a%20food%20forest%2C%20a%20place%20where%20every%20plant%20supports%20another%2C%20water%20is%20conserved%2C%20and%20the%20land%20heals%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abhishek%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20immersed%20himself%20in%20permaculture%20principles%2C%20learning%20to%20layer%20the%20landscape%20with%20tall%20canopy%20trees%2C%20like%20mangoes%2C%20guava%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20mid%E2%80%91level%20nitrogen%20fixers%20such%20as%20moringa%2C%20which%20he%20calls%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmiracle%20tree%2C%E2%80%9D%20because%20it%20grows%20fast%2C%20enriches%20soil%2C%20and%20feeds%20soil%20and%20people%20alike.%20It%20also%20had%20low%E2%80%91lying%20ground%20covers%20like%20sweet%20potato%2C%20sweet%20peas%2C%20butterfly%20pea%2C%20and%20brahmi%20to%20hold%20moisture%20and%20guard%20against%20erosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20remained%20the%20fiercest%20challenge%20for%20the%20young%20boy%2C%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20life%20on%20a%20farm%20in%20the%20Obulapuram%20village%20near%20Pamidi.%20The%20well%20had%20dried%20up%2C%20and%20the%20stream%20flowed%20only%20in%20the%20monsoon.%20So%20he%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20Neela%20Reddy%2C%20dug%20swales%2C%20trenches%20carved%20along%20the%20contours%20of%20the%20land%20to%20catch%20and%20hold