%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fiddlehead%20ferns%20in%20Assamese).%20My%20homestay%2C%20which%20I%20built%20myself%20using%20bamboo%20and%20mud%2C%20offers%20accommodation%20at%20Rs%201%2C500%20per%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20assistance%20from%20tourist%20guides%2C%20Sanatan%20is%20able%20to%20attract%20guests%20to%20his%20village.%20Although%20the%20monsoon%20season%20has%20currently%20paused%20his%20services%2C%20the%20last%20visitors%20arrived%20in%20March.%20Despite%20these%20pauses%2C%20running%20a%20homestay%20remains%20a%20viable%20means%20of%20livelihood%20for%20him.%20%E2%80%9CLast%20season%2C%20I%20earned%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000.%20Prior%20to%20running%20the%20homestay%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20daily%20wage%20labourer%20in%20tea%20gardens%2C%20earning%20merely%20Rs%20200%20a%20day.%20His%20efforts%20have%20truly%20transformed%20our%20lives%20for%20the%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FRajib-Assam-2-1752485454.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Local%20dishes%2C%20especially%20those%20prepared%20with%20local%20greens%20and%20rice%20cooked%20in%20bamboo%2C%20offer%20a%20taste%20of%20the%20unique%20culinary%20traditions%20of%20the%20area.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FRajib-Assam-2-1752485454.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FRajib-Assam-2-1752485454-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FRajib-Assam-2-1752485454-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FRajib-Assam-2-1752485454-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FRajib-Assam-2-1752