st%20food.%20The%20market%20is%20already%20full%20of%20that.%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20would%20not%20only%20nourish%20people%20but%20also%20give%20back%20to%20the%20environment%20and%20support%20our%20local%20farmers.%20It%20had%20to%20be%20rooted%20in%20purpose%20and%20not%20just%20profit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20COVID-19%20waves%20hit%2C%20which%20brought%20a%20pause%20to%20her%20usual%20routine%20and%20gave%20her%20a%20chance%20to%20rethink%20everything.%20As%20she%20watched%20the%20world%20buckle%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20disease%2C%20lifestyle%20disorders%2C%20and%20climate%20anxiety%2C%20she%20could%20not%20shake%20the%20feeling%20that%20food%20lay%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20it%20all.%20She%20began%20researching%20nutrition%2C%20agroecology%2C%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20neglected%20food%20heritage.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20research%20soon%20led%20her%20to%20focus%20on%20millets%20and%20organically%20grown%20vegetables%2C%20all%20tied%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20zero-waste%20lifestyle.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20more%20I%20read%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realised%20how%20powerful%20these%20grains%20are%2C%20not%20just%20for%20our%20health%20but%20for%20the%20planet%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CMillets%20require%20far%20less%20water%20and%20pesticides%20than%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250058%2Ffarmer-innovation-chintala-venkat-reddy-telangana-farmer-padma-shri-awardee-vitamin-d-rice-wheat-patent-wipo-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econventional%20crops%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20resilient%2C%20nutritious%2C%20and%20connected%20to%20our%20heritage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20understanding%20birthed%20a%20desire%20to%20bring%20these%20elements%20together%20in%20a%20thoughtful%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECooking%20with%20a%20conscience%