0workshops%2C%20children%20arrive%20as%20they%20are%2C%20curious%2C%20giggly%2C%20often%20indifferent%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98healthy%20eating.%E2%80%99%20They%20begin%20by%20visiting%20the%20cafe%E2%80%99s%20own%20kitchen%20garden%2C%20where%20they%20are%20taught%20to%20touch%20the%20soil%2C%20identify%20native%20herbs%20like%20%3Cem%3Etulsi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(holy%20basil)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebrahmi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20harvest%20spinach%2C%20edible%20flowers%2C%20or%20carrots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20step%20into%20the%20kitchen%2C%20washing%20fresh%20vegetables%20and%20observing%20the%20staff%20as%20they%20chop%20and%20prepare%20the%20ingredients.%20Guided%20by%20the%20team%2C%20they%20assemble%20their%20own%20salads%20and%20millet-based%20snacks%2C%20gaining%20hands-on%20experience.%20They%20even%20get%20the%20chance%20to%20work%20with%20local%20fruits%20and%20herbs%2C%20using%20methods%20like%20cold-press%20juicing%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318779%2Fmillet-summer-drink-simple-easy-recipes-sorghum-bajra-ragi-shakes-smoothie%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20fresh%20drinks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20also%20take%20part%20in%20sound%20healing%20and%20aromatherapy%20sessions%20before%20sitting%20down%20to%20eat%20mindfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095827.416_11zon-1752208145.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20classic%20vada%20pav%20is%20made%20from%20freshly%20baked%20ragi%20buns%20in%20the%20cafe%2C%20and%20it%20is%20very%20popular%20among%20customers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095827.416_11zon-1752208145.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095827.416_11zon-1752208145-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095827.416_11zon-1752208145-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095827.416_11zon-1752208145-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095827.416_11zon-1752208145-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467629%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20classic%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20made%20from%20freshly%20baked%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20buns%20in%20the%20cafe%2C%20and%20it%20is%20very%20popular%20among%20customers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20of%20these%20workshops%20is%20worth%20noting.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20come%20in%20scrunching%20their%20faces%20at%3Cem%3E%20ragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20vegetables%2C%20and%20they%20leave%20asking%20their%20parents%20for%20millet%20khichdi%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20cafe.%20Teachers%20report%20long-term%20behavioural%20changes%20in%20students%20who%20attended%20the%20workshops%3B%20some%20started%20home%20composting%2C%20others%20began%20reading%20food%20labels%20before%20purchasing%20snacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGradual%20small%20steps%20towards%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJahnavi%20shares%20that%20the%20workshop%20completely%20changed%20the%20way%20she%20thinks%20about%20food%20and%20the%20environment.%